commitResults.messageBody:
Complete Level 1: Echo, to enable my chatbot to echo back the inputs
user entered into my chatbot.

Implement an ArrayList from Java's List collection to store tasks.
Also implement add task function to the list.

My chatbot is now able to print out all the tasks stored in the
tasklist.

Add new files to make my code adhere to OOP principles.
Also implement mark as done feature to enable users to mark their
tasks as completed

Add Task Package for better encapsulation of task logic.
Add support for tracking ToDo, Deadline, and Event tasks. This includes
adding of tasks to tasklist.
Add parser functions to abstract parsing logic away from main code.
